name: geo.to
tag_list: mobile, lbs, website-builder, geosite, qr-code, mobile-sem
overview: geo.to is a technology company that enables anyone to Mobilize Locations™ through special purpose GeoSite mobile and online websites dedicated to any business or other location. geo.to’s patented GeoSite® and GeoLink® products and services enable businesses and other locations to provide instant, direct access to timely and accurate location information they own and control through all web services and traditional, digital and social media like Facebook, Twitter, SMS, emails, etc. geo.to provides The Easiest and Fastest Way to Find, Share and Interact With Locations™. geo.to’s ultimate objective is to improve the daily lives of billions of mobile phone and social media users as they find, share and interact with locations throughout the world.
